swaptrade_smartrouting_dialogue_desc_bes: We connect over 20 networks, 400 decentralized exchanges, and offer over 210,000 crypto assets in one place. This allows us to offer the largest variety of quotes on the market.

For bridge transactions: “Overall best” is the optimal route based on amount, network fees, slippage, and cross-chain bridge costs; “Fastest” is the quickest route; “Max amount” gets you the most tokens.
